1. *Gradnja zgrade* trajala je dve godine. (The construction of the building lasted two years.)
2. U centru grada se nalazi *zgrada* koja je izgrađena pre više decenija. (In the city center there is a building that was built more than a decade ago.)
3. *Zgrade* su bile uskoro gotove. (The buildings were soon finished.)
4. Na obodu grada se nalazi nekoliko *zgrada*. (On the outskirts of the city there are several buildings.)
5. Oni su *zgradu* popravili za nekoliko meseci. (They fixed the building in a few months.)
6. Oni su *zgradu* počeli da gradi još prošle godine. (They started building the building last year.)